<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="base"><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord">5<sup><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist"><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">4 </span></span></span></span></span></span></sup></span><span class="mrel">= </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">25 </span><span class="mbin">Ã— </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">25 </span><span class="mbin">Ã— </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">25 </span><span class="mbin">Ã— </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">25 </span><span class="mrel">= </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">390</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mord">625</span></span></p>
<p>The sum of the strings less the number of strings without a &#8216;x&#8217; indicates how many strings actually contain at least one &#8216;x&#8217;:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="base"><span class="mord">456</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mord">976 </span><span class="mbin">âˆ’ </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">390</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mord">625 </span><span class="mrel">= </span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">66</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mord">351</span></span></p>
<p>There are 66,351 strings of four lowercase letters that contain at least one &#8216;x&#8217;.</p>
